message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $120. I believe it's a great deal and would be very useful for you.
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I understand the value of the product, but I am only able to pay up to $95. I hope we can come to an agreement.
Thanks for your offer, Bob. I appreciate your interest. How about we meet in the middle at $105?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I'm still not able to go above $95 for the product. I hope we can find a mutual agreement.
